form_title.ms_form_title_llm_v1: Title: TRANSLATION OF A BIRTH CERTIFICATE, Form Number: AA 711483

full_text: Screened by NARA, 8/11/2023 TRANSLATION OF A BIRTH CERTIFICATE NAME: Elizabeth Eliane Heraux SEX: Female DATE OF BIRTH: November 19, 1943 PLACE OF BIRTH: Port-Au-Prince, Haiti NAME OF FATHER: Georges Heraux NAME OF MOTHER: Gertrude Kalmar NAME OF PATERNAL GRANDFATHER: NAME OF PATERNAL GRANDMOTHER: NAME OF MATERNAL GRANDFATHER: NAME OF MATERNAL GRANDMOTHER: COURT: National Archives - Haiti PAGE: 10 VOLUME: 923 WITNESSES: Haus Kalmar and Roger Denis JUDGE: Laurore St. Juste M.. A. I CERTIFY THAT THE ABOVE IS A FAITHFUL EXTRACT OF THE RELEVANT INFORMATION IN THE ATTACHED DOCUMENT AND THAT I AM A QUALIFIED TRANSLATOR CONVERSANT WITH BOTH LANGUAGES. Liba Heram State of Florida / County of DADE SIGNATURE OF TRANSLATOR The 7/10 foregoing instrument was acknowledged before me this who has produced a 1992 by Dizabeth Heraux as and who not) take an oath. Reynold Heraux (Notary signature) AA 711483 PUBLIC OFFICIAL NOTARY SEAL REYNOLD HERAUX COMMISSION NUMBER AA 711483 FLORD MY COMMISSION EXP. OCT. 1,1993
